org.spongepowered.api.math

Interface Vector3f

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Vector3f>, java.io.Serializable

    public interface Vector3f
extends java.lang.Comparable<Vector3f>, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Represent a 3 component vector using floats. It is immutable and all vectors returned by the methods are new instances.
